      <section id="id1169521381766">
        <title>Mary’s Naughty Brothers</title>
        <list id="id1169524140894" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Do you think your brothers and sisters are naughty? </item>
          <item>Read the story of Mary and her naughty brothers. </item>
        </list>
        <para id="id1169524466192">My name is Mary. I live in a big house with my mom and dad and my two brothers. They are so naughty. My mom has to shout at them a lot. One day they hid Daddy’s keys. He was late for work. I think he wanted to smack them. But Mom said that they must wash his car for him. Dad said they must do it for a whole year.</para>
        <para id="id1169531635430">Mom takes us to school. She does not go to work. She works in the house at home. I help her when I get home from school. We cook supper together. My brothers don’t help us. They just make a mess. </para>
        <para id="id6389372">Mommy says she will just lie in bed one day to see what happens.</para>
