        <para id="id5724328">Let’s look at words</para>
        <para id="id1169525841551">Remember the vowels A E I O U. Sometimes Y has to work as a vowel too. Find the words that end in “y”. Y does not make the same sound as when we begin a word like YOU. What is the sound it makes in the words you have found. List them in the box below. </para>
